---
import SauceSVG from './SauceSVG.astro';
---
<section class="features">
  <SauceSVG
    id="sauce2"
    sauceStyle="top:40px;right:-80px;width:520px;height:260px;"
    viewBox="0 0 520 260"
    d="M510,40 C420,170 330,-20 240,110 S70,210 10,120"
  />
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <h2>Cosa trovi dentro</h2>
      <p>Tutto quello che serve per mangiare lurido e felice.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid2">

      <article class="card reveal">
        <div class="ic">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 21s7-6.5 7-12a7 7 0 1 0-14 0c0 5.5 7 12 7 12Z"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Mappa calda</h3>
        <p>Geo-localizzazione real-time. Filtri intelligenti: aperto ora, veggie, 4+★ e vicino a te.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="card reveal">
        <div class="ic">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 3l2.5 5.5L20 9l-4 4 1 6-5-3-5 3 1-6-4-4 5.5-.5L12 3Z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Recensioni vere</h3>
        <p>Community verificata, moderazione crowdsourced e zero bot. Solo chi mangia davvero.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="card reveal">
        <div class="ic">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="6" y="2.5" width="12" height="19" rx="2.5"/>
            <line x1="10.5" y1="18.5" x2="13.5" y2="18.5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>iOS + Android</h3>
        <p>App nativa con dark mode di serie e notifiche push geolocalizzate quando passi vicino a un lurido.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="card reveal">
        <div class="ic">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M7 4h10v4a5 5 0 0 1-10 0V4Z"/>
            <path d="M7 5H4v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3M17 5h3v2a3 3 0 0 1-3 3"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="13" x2="12" y2="17"/>
            <path d="M8.5 20.5h7l-1-3.5h-5l-1 3.5Z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Gamification</h3>
        <p>Badge, XP e 5 livelli: da Novice del panino a Re del Lurido. Più condividi, più sali.</p>
      </article>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
